    <item>
      <title>分析师称，公投后十年来，英国脱欧已经损害了英国经济增长</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/23/business/brexit-uk-economy.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以贸易和投资下降为由，分析师普遍认为，英国经济规模比英国留在欧盟时的规模要小。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/23/business/brexit-uk-economy.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 12:42:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
